  "body": "\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-df143a919eb5a047b3fd61fd7e2f63f4 wp-block-paragraph\">SiteFlow is available on three platforms — the mobile app, the web portal, and the website. You can use any of them based on what you need to do.</p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-1e1f1d00a2215e5f903b4a23baa257bf\">Official Website</h2>\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-a60b5a4fb5387c635472b4f7acec6397 wp-block-paragraph\">The SiteFlow website is: <strong><a href=\"https://siteflow.com/\">https://siteflow.com/</a></strong></p>\n<p class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-b442bdcdc05f12cc8f5e2f252d8fc71a wp-block-paragraph\">Visit the website to learn about features, pricing, and to get in touch with the team.</p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large has-custom-border\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-palette-color-3-border-color wp-image-52333\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"477\" src=\"/images/recon/Screenshot-2026-05-05-at-2.22.27-PM-1-1-1024x477.webp\" style=\"border-top-left-radius:6px;border-top-right-radius:6px;border-bottom-left-radius:6px;border-bottom-right-radius:6px\" width=\"1024\"/></figure>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-66bbc180dcb7dcf560f5564c9e438fd3\">Web Portal — Desktop and Browser Access</h2>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">To use SiteFlow on a desktop or laptop, open your browser and go to: <strong><a href=\"https://web.siteflow.com/\">https://web.siteflow.com/</a></strong></p>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized has-custom-border is-style-default wp-duotone-unset-1\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"has-border-color has-palette-color-3-border-color wp-image-52331\" decoding=\"async\" height=\"1024\" src=\"/images/recon/Screenshot-2026-05-05-at-2.23.03-PM-913x1024.webp\" style=\"border-top-left-radius:8px;border-top-right-radius:8px;border-bottom-left-radius:8px;border-bottom-right-radius:8px;aspect-ratio:0.8916132627472834;width:402px;height:auto\" width=\"913\"/></figure>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Log in using your registered mobile number and the OTP sent to it. Everything you can do in the mobile app is also available on the web portal.</p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-64dd62c8b8c625e3c2a09ffcb0608d76\">Mobile App — Android</h2>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Search <strong>“SiteFlow”</strong> on the Google Play Store, or use the direct link below:</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.app.SiteFlow\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.app.SiteFlow</a></p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-2dd9bbff258b50219c221d46839dfe97\">Mobile App — iOS (iPhone and iPad)</h2>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">Search <strong>“SiteFlow Construction App”</strong> on the Apple App Store, or use the direct link below:</p>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"><a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/in/app/SiteFlow-construction-app/id6443621595\">https://apps.apple.com/in/app/SiteFlow-construction-app/id6443621595</a></p>\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-black-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-ac09f1c8e71b0fe6010b620687efff40\">Which Platform Should You Use?</h2>\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table is-style-stripes\"><table class=\"has-palette-color-4-color has-text-color has-link-color has-border-color has-palette-color-3-border-color has-fixed-layout\"><thead><tr><th>Platform</th><th>Best For</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Mobile App</td><td>Site supervisors, field staff, day-to-day attendance and DPR</td></tr><tr><td>Web Portal</td><td>Admins, accountants, project managers — detailed data entry and reports</td></tr><tr><td>Website</td><td>Learning about SiteFlow, requesting demos, contacting sales</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>\n"
}